title: Are you OK, aunty May? China warms to UK prime minster
text:
Are you OK, aunty May? China warms to UK prime minster Friday, February 02, 2018 - 02:08 
Britain's Prime Minister won 9 billion pounds in trade deals during a 3 day visit to China this week. She also picked up a new nickname - 'Aunty May'. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
